Titolo: The Dwarves (video game)

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: The Dwarves is a fantasy tactical role-playing video game developed by King Art Games. It features music composed by Benny Oschmann. In the game, players must find their way through various maze-like, medieval environments while battling a variety of monsters using a wide array of weapons. It is based on the novel The Dwarves, by Markus Heitz.
A beta version of the game was released on June 3, 2016.There was a campaign on Kickstarter that raised $310,091 for the development of the game through 2015 and 2016. The Dwarves will be published by EuroVideo Medien and made available on GOG.com.

Genere: Tactical role-playing game

Valutazione: N/A
